{"tid":905183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"疑偷單車擸刀斬人 4南亞男被捕","createTime":"2018-11-17T02:43:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T02:55:17.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1208307dc3261422b03578d78381a432895d0c0d","tid":905183,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T02:43:50.000Z","msg":"一名男子早前在油麻地被人偷走一輛單車，懷疑是露宿加士居道近渡船街天橋底的南亞男子所為，凌晨1時許，事主聯同數名友人，到天橋底與南亞男交涉，其間雙方發生爭執。數名南亞男子衝出，持牛肉刀向他們追斬，事主走避不及，腳部中刀受傷。<br />\n<br />\n逃脫的友人協助報警，西九龍衝鋒隊趕至，在天橋底一間屋內，拘捕四名涉案南亞男子，並在一個尼龍篋內搜獲兩把牛肉刀。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181117/58923639\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181117%2F58923639&d=QYXNQwZXmojV2I8RYOZGh54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=3eeb858d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181117%2F58923639&h=29167cf3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181117/58923639</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181117/large/1542395142_5d9d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181117%2Flarge%2F1542395142_5d9d.jpg&h=af8358bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181117/large/1542395193_0839.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181117%2Flarge%2F1542395193_0839.jpg&h=4c9d5768&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181117/large/1542395272_db13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181117%2Flarge%2F1542395272_db13.jpg&h=928a3d7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181117/58923639\" da